<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٤٦٩ -<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الْحُمَيْدِيُّ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ: حَدَّثَنَا عَمْرٌو،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ <span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>كُنَّا مَعَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فِي سَفَرٍ، وَكُنْتُ عَلَى بَكْرٍ صَعْبٍ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> لِعُمَرَ:</span> <span class="c2">(بِعْنِيهِ)</span>. فَابْتَاعَهُ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(هُوَ لَكَ يَا عَبْدَ اللَّهِ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٢٠٠٩]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>